      "data": {
        "title": "Ports Expose",
        "body": "A port tells the outside world what this graph makes available.\n\nIt is an addressable contract, not the thing doing the navigation.\n\nA good port usually has:\n- graph identity\n- a real surface payload\n- an honest role such as `card`, `port`, or `document`",
        "tag": "Concept",
