        "title": "Ports Are Addressed",
        "body": "A portal or another graph artifact targets a port by identity.\n\nUse the shape `filePath#nodeId:portId` when you are addressing a specific port node.\n\nExample:\n`github://twilite-zone/public/tutorial/basic-primitives/port/root.node#port-primitive-reader:root`\n\nThat is what lets a graph expose multiple meaningful surfaces without ambiguity.",
        "tag": "Concept",
