        "title": "What Success Looks Like",
        "body": "A correct outcome has:\n- a declaration with a real surface entry\n- a port with `identity.graphId`\n- a real target or a clearly declared reader surface\n- one real payload kind (`markdown`, `svg`, or `html`)\n- no `renderShape.kind: card`\n- no markdownified `xmlns` inside SVG",
        "status": "verify",
